query:
INSERT INTO station 
        (api_id, gr_id, link, titel, trojanergefahr, typ, 
        zp_start, vg_id, zp_modifiziert, gremium_isff)
        VALUES
        ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5,
        (SELECT id FROM stationstyp WHERE value = $6), $7, $8, 
        COALESCE($9, NOW()), $10)
        RETURNING station.id
